OL,4,G2100FCaptain Phillips
OL,5,     GTom Hanks gazes anxiously, from
OL,6,     Gthe vessel's bow. Barkhad Abdi's
OL,7,     Gpirates board; he's the captain
OL,8,     Gnow. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,9,G2340FOld
OL,10,     GPart horror and part mystery.
OL,11,     GCouples trapped beside the sea.
OL,12,     GAgeing exponentially. It's
OL,13,     Gcomplex but you'll get the gist.
OL,14,     GAnd it's Shyamalan, so there's a
OL,15,     Gtwist. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,16,G0150FHearts of Darkness: A Filmmaker's
OL,17,     FApocalypse
OL,18,     GDocumentary charting the problems
OL,19,     Gthat plagued the Apocalypse Now
OL,20,     Gshoot, threatening this cinematic
OL,21,     Glandmark, Coppola's career and
OL,22,     Geven one actor's life.
